The Finance Ministry said it proposed tothe underwriting syndicate a record low 4.7 pct coupon on the10-year government bond to be issued in April, down from theprevious record low five pct March issue.    The bond would be priced at 99.75 to yield 4.736 pctcompared with 99.50 and 5.075 pct in March, and proposed issuevolume is 1,400 billion yen against 475 billion, it said.    The syndicate is expected to accept the terms immediately,underwriters said. REUTER&#3;